🍀we try our personal best in everything we do. We always try to make ourselves proud and do our best work.

🍀we cheer each other on. 

🍀 we are a family. We care for one another, and take care of one another.

🍀we have the sweetest class!

We also use our class fish jar from @texturesbymaria for whole group compliments - both in and out of the classroom. The best buy in for this is allowing students to choose the prize they earn as a class team.

✨Calendar Math Magic ✨

What math routines do you focus on in K?

As part of our calendar math time, we practice a number of the day with:

- tens frames 
- tallies
- coins on a 🐷 bank
- number bond
- place value blocks
- a number line

For the first 10 days, I do this on the Smart Board and the kids watch.

Then, we do this together. I write on the Smart Board while the kids use their calendar math journals.

Eventually, calendar math time is completely student - led. They pick the number for each focus and choose a peer to model the number on the Smart Board. 

We start with numbers 1-10, then move into teen numbers and beyond.

It's a great way to build key number sense skills to set kids up for success in math!
